data.description: Come see this beautiful home located in Franklin Local School District! This home was newly renovated in 2020-21. Renovations include new electric, insulation, windows, exterior doors, gutters, metal roof, back decking boards, flooring, paint, kitchen cabinets, countertops, backsplash, central air, and a hot water tank. The outside siding was also painted. A huge detached garage provides extra storage space or could be the perfect place to work.
